OMG I feel really stupid. I got confused between Kattey and Cheene re Mora :( Sorry about that. 
But yea, I personally do not like autotune and this does sound like a Bollywood song if you remove Ustad's voice. If I wanted to listen to a Bollywood song by Salim Suleman, I would listen to the hundreds there are out there. The reason why I (and I am sure many others) loaded up this video is to watch something different. This is where Coke Studio Pakistan does it right. They focus more on the classical part rather than the modern part.
